Removed reference to "Big Four". That article is now called "Big Tech" and talks about various groups of big tech companies, because it turns out that there is no consistently defined "Big Four". Some newer articles group together the MAGA companies as the "Big Four" (Microsoft, Apple, Google, Amazon), while older articles group the GAFA companies (replacing Microsoft with Facebook). And other articles group the "Big Five" (GAFAM). These groupings are subjective and there is no consensus.
